relation: Darrow4 - #11 Prince Poo, after a few words from his Master, sets out for his final training.
Darrow4 - #12 After some reflecting and interaction with the villagers, Poo reaches his destination. Will the powerful "Moo" training bring him success...?
Darrow4 - #13 The old sage appears and disappears just as quickly as the wind. What sort of powers will he awaken in Poo? He can start with "turn into a tornado and fly away", for one.
Darrow4 - #14 Poo begins his training, which requires deep concentration and meditation. While there is a minor distraction, he has yet to encounter the greatest distraction of all.
Darrow4 - #15 With the start of the training, Poo is faced with a far more deadly encounter than he could have imagined.
